Bosse_Chaos_Status_Down For The Count_De: Unable to move or execute actions.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Accretion_De: Plagued by rapidly hardening mud. All HP recovery is reduced. Effect dissipates once fully healed.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Dynamic Flui: Plagued by a chaotic body of water that will deal damage when the effect ends.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Entropy_Desc: Plagued by chaotic flames that will deal damage to nearby party members when the effect ends.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Filthy_Desc: Earthen residue is causing damage over time.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Headwind_Des: Plagued by chaotic frontal winds that will deal damage when the effect ends. Effect dissipates upon exposure to directional winds. Knockback effects from winds faced head-on are doubled, while those of rear winds are reduced by half.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Primordial C: Plagued by rapidly hardening mud. Damage taken is reduced, but all HP recovery is nullified. Effect dissipates when damage that would cause HP to drop below 0 is taken, leaving HP at 1.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Tailwind_Des: Plagued by chaotic rear winds that will deal damage when the effect ends. Effect dissipates upon exposure to directional winds. Knockback effects from winds faced head-on are reduced by half, while those of rear winds are doubled.
ContentDesc_Alphametrie 1.0: The switch taunts you. You cannot resist. A satisfying “click” and your moment of weakness has activated a new phase of the Savage Initiative. This time, however, something is different. The broadcast is interrupted by an unexpected transmission─a message from beyond oblivion. A familiar voice guides you in an unfamiliar tone, and arms you with knowledge of impossible simulations. Your evolution is at hand.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_20000_Text: Grovel in terror! The flames hunger for your flesh!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_20001_Text: Scurry and flail, little mortals! The raging tide will claim you all!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_20002_Text: Despair at your hollow fate! The winds will strip away your skin!
